{"tid":935534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"SORRY SIR 再現 我喺警察部嘅恥辱","createTime":"2018-12-10T05:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T06:11:44.000Z","uid":167928,"like":433,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f95d57926487af2da3f7cc6fd71baa32c45f97","tid":935534,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:47:12.000Z","msg":"【警署奇警】SORRY SIR再現 持紙牌站觀塘警署<br />\n1小時前8.2K<br />\n即時突發<br />\n<br />\n因手持「SORRY SIR」紙牌而人氣爆燈的觀塘警署軍裝警員「番薯」，今日又再現身。他手持寫上「SORRY SIR 我喺警察部嘅恥辱」紙牌，站在觀塘警署入口。<br />\n<br />\n今日上午11時半左右，有市民出入觀塘警署時，見到「SORRY SIR」。記者到場，果然見到他站在警署門前，手拿着一張過膠A4紙，白底黑字寫上：「SORRY SIR 我喺警察部嘅恥辱」。他沒有陀槍，只是着記者向警察公共關係科了解詳情，至中午12時15分左右，他返回警署內。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JoF5Zih.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJoF5Zih.png&h=49b5f1f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ki3LYs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ki3LYs.png&h=0b3cd4ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2b92a225b68566de4f2f7fc3e7735a9b69f4a0d","tid":935534,"uid":167928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48aa11d4b7b3c6bd56af6aaed50809fc8c4ce3d","tid":935534,"uid":153689,"like":351,"dislike":3,"score":348,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"警犬弱智夠未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da08982678b18a315211f53e890efbbaa390888d","tid":935534,"uid":32782,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T05:50:35.000Z","msg":"又來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9651a282aeb2ed1bc18a357f65